{"tid":350190,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「星爵」Chris Pratt與安娜費莉絲驚爆離婚","createTime":"2017-08-07T05:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T16:13:59.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fac687a6766bc86670f9d3a7a7d843bb5c016ae","tid":350190,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"漫威超級英雄電影《銀河守護隊》（Guardians of the Galaxy）系列飾演「星爵」的38歲男星Chris Pratt與40歲女星安娜費莉絲（Anna Faris）一直是荷里活模範夫妻，不過周日卻驚爆離婚！&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩人於社交網站發出離婚聲明：「安娜同我好遺憾宣布，我哋要離婚。我哋努力咗好耐，而我哋都好失望。我哋個仔有兩個好愛佢嘅家長，為咗佢，我哋之後想將呢個情況保持愈私人愈好。我哋仍然愛對方，會珍惜一齊嘅時光，繼續畀對方最深嘅尊重。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nChris與安娜於2007年合作喜劇《Take Me Home Tonight》時撻著，當時安娜仍與前夫Ben Indra結婚，同年安娜申請離婚。Chris與安娜於2008年訂婚，2009年於峇里島結婚。兩人的兒子Jack於2012年8月出世。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安娜最出名的作品是4套《搞乜鬼奪命雜作》（Scary Movie）電影，Chris的星途則一直平平，直到近年因為《銀河守護隊》才彈起，之後又主演《侏羅紀世界》（Jurassic World）。Chris於2015年與金像影后珍妮花羅倫絲（Jennifer Lawrence）主演《太空潛航者》（Passengers），一度傳出緋聞，安娜受訪時曾回應表示即使緋聞是假，也令她大受打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170807/mobile/bkn-20170807114904028-0807_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170807%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170807114904028-0807_00862_001.html&d=8kwyYxWn41c2N58G8jocGS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ee4e7a3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170807/mobile/bkn-20170807114904028-0807_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"041934c68fe4f27982783c22ce07e879f230f336","tid":350190,"uid":127269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T05:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a92a3bf7c2c923e31a6b9b13f2769a3fa2b8675","tid":350190,"uid":17081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T06:03:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"